lemma nth_least_lift[simp]: "nth_least (lift A) 0 = 0" "enat n < esize A \<Longrightarrow> nth_least (lift A) (Suc n) = Suc (nth_least A n)"
unfolding lift_def
by (auto simp add: enat_0_iff conj_commute)
